| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1406 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b1c46bc5-ee5a-5a56-899a-e6b03e47858d"
